{"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"anchor":"Short-Answer","level":2,"text":"Short Answer","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Yes, the FreemiumKit SDK ships with a built-in parental gate. Just call ","type":"text"},{"code":"FreemiumKit.shared.enableParentalGate(options:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" upon app start.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Full-Answer","level":2,"text":"Full Answer","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"We‚Äôve built a simple math-based parental gate that will ask a random multiplication question with numbers from 2 to 10. This should be easy enough for any parent to solve, but tricky enough to avoid small children (6 or younger) accidentally getting into the paywall, as required by the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/app-store\/review\/guidelines\/#kids-category","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" for apps in the Kids category.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Just tell our SDK that it should use a parental gate before showing the paywall upon app start, like this:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["import FreemiumKit","","@main","struct AwesomeApp: App {","   init() {","      FreemiumKit.shared.enableParentalGate(options: ParentalGateOptions())","   }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This single line will already work! üéâ But it will use the default system colors (black\/white\/accent) which can look off."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You probably want to customize the parental gate to look nicer to fit your apps playful color scheme, like this:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["import FreemiumKit","","@main","struct AwesomeApp: App {","  init() {","    FreemiumKit.shared.enableParentalGate(","      options: ParentalGateOptions(","         background: .linearGradient(","            LinearGradient(","               gradient: Gradient(colors: [.blue, .purple]),","               startPoint: .topLeading, ","               endPoint: .bottomTrailing","            )","         ),","         textColor: .white, ","         submitButtonBackgroundColor: .green,","         submitButtonTitleColor: .white","      )","    )","  }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The result will look like this on iOS (and similar on other platforms):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"ParentalGate-Customized"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/freemiumkit.app","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Contact","level":2,"text":"Contact","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Have questions or need support? Reach out to me at ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"mailto:freemiumkit@fline.dev"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Legal","level":2,"text":"Legal","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Cihat G√ºnd√ºz ¬© 2024. All rights reserved."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Privacy: No personal data is tracked on this site."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/www.fline.dev\/imprint\/","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"small"}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"FAQs","role":"sampleCode","title":"Are ‚ÄòMade for Kids‚Äô apps supported with a Parental Gate?"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/FreemiumKit\/documentation\/Index","doc:\/\/FreemiumKit\/documentation\/FreemiumKit\/FAQs"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Learn how to use our built-in parental gate for apps ‚ÄòMade for Kids‚Äô to comply with Apples guidelines and avoid accidental purchases by small children."}],"sections":[],"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/FreemiumKit\/documentation\/FreemiumKit\/FAQ-HowItWorks",